{"tid":415721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果借啲騎推支那寶微訊，我就會企的士佬嗰邊反你！","createTime":"2017-09-27T08:22:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-28T08:28:57.000Z","uid":41245,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4562d6de96eff26b45bba9e6a812fb59831ee15a","tid":415721,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T08:22:36.000Z","msg":"橫掂我都可以call相熟的、Uber㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲仆街的士司機我可以好易就避到<br />\n但依家個輿論想借的士佬引入支那寶/微訊？不了<br />\n支那寶/微訊一入市場一定好難避<br />\n係未有其他電子支付款到市場（八達通、tng、Apple pay-visa master cardless）我係唔會中伏幫你推電子付款㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打手唔洗扮晒嘢拎的士佬嚟祭旗啦！！！<br />\n<br />\n我係幫濕鳩的士佬都唔幫你支那嘢呀！我撐濕鳩陀地都唔撐支共呀！"},{"pid":"aae089c1914d4fb83eabce024c6792a1086df949","tid":415721,"uid":41245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T08:23:31.000Z","msg":"標題：借啲咦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好打唔打打咗個騎出嚟"},{"pid":"da73041a8f37b861245a0b8039190f1d656a6404","tid":415721,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T08:27:30.000Z","msg":"個輿論好明顯係想借啲咦話「為咗打擊的士濫收，所以規定全面要有支那寶/微訊option」<br />\n如果係噉，我一定會企係的士佬嗰面！"},{"pid":"cc06b3fd5d9262212476fbe1f0134b7d925b6f15","tid":415721,"uid":112502,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T08:27:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>橫掂我都可以call相熟的、Uber㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n啲仆街的士司機我可以好易就避到<br />\n但依家個輿論想借的士佬引入支那寶/微訊？不了<br />\n支那寶/微訊一入市場一定好難避<br />\n係未有其他電子支付款到市場（八達通、tng、Apple pay-visa master cardless）我係唔會中伏幫你推電子付款㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n打手唔洗